OL,3,CResidents 'heartbroken' and 'angry' as
OL,4,Cquarry expansion approved
OL,6,FPeople living in Glyncoch, near
OL,7,FPontypridd say they're worried about
OL,8,Ftheir children's safety because of
OL,9,Fblasts from a quarry near their homes.
OL,11,FThey are taking a petition to the
OL,12,FSenedd to to stop the expansion of
OL,13,FCraig-y-Hesg quarry and want new laws
OL,14,Fto be passed so this doesn't happen to
OL,15,Fanother community.
OL,17,FClaire Allen has lived in Glyncoch her
OL,18,Fwhole life and showed us this video of
OL,19,Fone of the blasts.
