OL,6,F"This mountain is a part of our
OL,7,Fchildhood, and they've put a fence
OL,8,Faround it. It's ours, and it just
OL,9,Fmakes me upset. Our lives have been
OL,10,Fput on hold because of this," she said.
OL,12,FSelena Young has also lived in
OL,13,FGlyncoch her whole life. She says if
OL,14,Fthe expansion goes ahead, the quarry
OL,15,Fwill be within 158 metres of her house.
OL,17,F"I couldn't sit and wait for things to
OL,18,Fhappen. It's just ridiculous that it's
OL,19,Fallowed to happen and I needed to know
OL,20,Fwhy," she said.
