OL,6,F"I'm still not coming to terms with
OL,7,Fit. It's devastating. I used to walk
OL,8,Fmy dogs along that mountain, and to go
OL,9,Fup there now and see the fence - it's
OL,10,Fgut-wrenching, it's heartbreaking to
OL,11,Fsee. Where we used to play as
OL,12,Fchildren, the trees - they've all been
OL,13,Ftaken down.
OL,15,F"I can see it from my back garden and
OL,16,FI see it everyday and it really angers
OL,17,Fme."
