OL,3,CResidents 'heartbroken' and 'angry' as
OL,4,Cquarry expansion approved
OL,6,FThe quarry has been there since 1885,
OL,7,Fbut in 2020, its owners Heidelberg
OL,8,FMaterials applied for permission to
OL,9,Fextend the sandstone quarry from
OL,10,FRhondda Cynon Taf council, but were
OL,11,Funsuccessful.
OL,13,FOperations were meant to end in
OL,14,FDecember 2022, but the company
OL,15,Fappealed the decision, and the Welsh
OL,16,Fgovernment approved the extension.
OL,18,FThey now hope to extract an additional
OL,19,F15.7 million tonnes of rock at a rate
OL,20,Fof 400,000 tonnes per year until 2047.
