OL,3,CResidents 'heartbroken' and 'angry' as
OL,4,Cquarry expansion approved
OL,6,FA petition for a 1000 metre mandatory
OL,7,Fbuffer zone for all new and existing
OL,8,Fquarries has over 11,000 signatures,
OL,9,Fand has received cross-party support.
OL,11,FChris Whiles has lived in the area for
OL,12,F15 years and says it is losing a part
OL,13,Fof its culture with the loss of green
OL,14,Fspace.
OL,16,F"It's us, it's Welsh culture. We're
OL,17,Fknown for our mountains, for our
OL,18,Fluscious greens," he said.
