OL,6,F"Whats heartbreaking is we're in the
OL,7,Fbottom 5% of deprived areas in Wales,
OL,8,Fso we do our best, we stick together,
OL,9,Fand they're taking this away from us -
OL,10,Fthe little that we've got and they've
OL,11,Fripped it from us."
OL,13,FHe says since the expansion has begun,
OL,14,Fthe blasts from the quarry have
OL,15,Fstarted to affect the community more.
OL,17,F"Years ago you wouldn't notice, you'd
OL,18,Fthink something had dropped upstairs,
OL,19,Fbut now it's shaking, the houses
OL,20,Fshake."
