OL,6,FHe shares others concerns for the
OL,7,Fsafety of their children, and is
OL,8,Fconscious of other industrial
OL,9,Fdisasters, not far way in the area's
OL,10,Fpast.
OL,12,F"When you hear your child say, 'Is my
OL,13,Fschool going to fall down?', what's
OL,14,Fthe first thing you think of? Aberfan.
OL,15,FAnd to us in South Wales that means a
OL,16,Flot. "
OL,18,FDoug Williams has been a Councillor
OL,19,Ffor Glyncoch since 2008 and is
OL,20,Fconcerned for the health of future
OL,21,Fgenerations.
