OL,6,F"I won't be around in 2047, when the
OL,7,Fquarrying is meant to end, but the
OL,8,Fyoungsters will," he said.
OL,10,F"I myself have been diagnosed with
OL,11,FCOPD and emphysema. There's children
OL,12,Fin school with asthma - five, six,
OL,13,Fseven years old.
OL,15,FHe believes that, because the area is
OL,16,Fan ex-council estate, it's not being
OL,17,Fvalued properly.
OL,19,F"It probably wouldn't happen in
OL,20,Faffluent areas, they wouldn't allow
OL,21,Fit," he said.
