OL,6,FA Rhondda Cynon Taf Council
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "We refused
OL,8,Fplanning permission to expand the
OL,9,Fquarry's operation in 2020, and Hanson
OL,10,Fsubsequently exercised its right to
OL,11,Flodge an appeal against that decision.
OL,13,F"The Council's decision was then
OL,14,Foverturned by Welsh Ministers, who
OL,15,Fgranted planning permission for the
OL,16,Fwestern extension of the quarry.
