OL,6,FHeidelberg materials, who own the
OL,7,Fquarry said: "Blasting, like all
OL,8,Faspects of quarrying, is highly
OL,9,Fregulated, and the UK has stringent
OL,10,Flevels in place. Operating within
OL,11,Fthese standards across all our
OL,12,Fquarries, means that quarry blasts
OL,13,Fpose no risk to people or property.
